@HostAddress = http://localhost:5277

### Create Order
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "idempotencyKey": "unique-order-key-12345",
  "items": [
    {
      "productId": "9b0f1a23-4567-89ab-cdef-0123456789ab",
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get Order Details
@orderId = 3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Cancel Order
PUT {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/cancel
Accept: application/json

###

### List Customer Orders
@customerId = 3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
GET {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders/customer/{{customerId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Retry Failed Order
POST {{HostAddress}}/api/v1/orders/{{orderId}}/retry
Accept: application/json

###
